<p>英 /'ɔːdəli/    美 /'ɔːrdərli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>整齐的；有条理的；守秩序的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Traffic lights are there to guide traffic <strong>in an orderly way</strong>.
红绿灯的存在是为了有序地引导交通。</p><footer>译林⑦ – 4</footer></div></div>